{
  "stem": "25809.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I cut that argument short by saying, I'm going to Australia, and you guys can get your divorce.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I couldn't get into the United States, where I wanted to go, because that was a three-year waiting list.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was in a hurry to get out, because I didn't want to go into the army either.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because then I would have to go into the army for three years, and I was afraid I wouldn't learn anything in the army.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said, I'd-- I'd rather be somewhere else where I can work and make a living for myself than these three years in the Army and be stuck in the Dutch Army here.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Of course, the Dutch Army in those years was certainly not very popular, and I'm not sure if it is popular at the moment either.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Though the-- it has-- they have reduced the time that you have to spend in the army.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But to spend three years in the army, that's a hell of a long time when you had just lost four and a half years in the war.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I felt I didn't want to lose any more time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I managed to get my papers within about-- I was just turning 18, and it took me about eight months, and I got my papers for Australia.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so everybody came to say goodbye to me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was going to take the train from Centraal Station to go to Marseilles where I would pick up a ship called the and where I would go and board that would sail to Australia.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the last words of my father when I was there at the station, he says, OK, show me you're worth something.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was his goodbye to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
